name: jakuzure nonon all outfits | Kill la Kill KlK
description:
Main trigger word is jakuzure nonon

Lora power is around 0.6-0.9

For her school outfit use (jakuzure nonon), shako cap, uniform, tassel

For orchestra suit use (jakuzure nonon), heart, (heart pad), orchestra suit, (strapless bottom), (underboob), speakers_wings. Speakers_wings might work not so well sometimes. And put more priority to heart pad tag for her heart sticker on her crotch

For her sportswear (jakuzure nonon), (track jacket), (red buruma), (pink soft hat)

And for nudist beach one (jakuzure nonon), (black soft hat), (holster), (black gloves),(utility belt),(shoulder holster)

Black and pink soft hat tags are custom one. Use it if you want hat one
